{"tid":766650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美中貿易戰升級　兩國高層根本「零接觸」","createTime":"2018-08-03T18:04:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T05:31:53.000Z","uid":147314,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"19490d2a25cd97e45c4eed4b1850e5c910e7755b","tid":766650,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T18:04:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2018/08/03/there-is-zero-engagement-between-us-and-china-as-trade-tensions-esca.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2Fthere-is-zero-engagement-between-us-and-china-as-trade-tensions-esca.html&d=NJFQozuEa1L2v%2BllVAc0jm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=ce27cec1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2018/08/03/there-is-zero-engagement-between-us-and-china-as-trade-tensions-esca.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>There is 'zero' engagement between US and China as trade tensions escalate, official says</strong><br />\n<br />\nA senior administration official told CNBC on Friday that there was &quot;zero&quot; engagement between the Trump administration and China as the two countries ratchet up trade tensions.<br />\n<br />\nThe official said that there had been &quot;one call in the past few days,&quot; and that it resolved nothing."},{"pid":"767294eac348c92113038afff79601e591df9e1e","tid":766650,"uid":147314,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T18:05:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1908077/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F1908077%2F&d=NJFQozuEa1L2v%2BllVAc0jm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=ff495afb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1908077/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>中美貿易爭端升級 兩國高層「零接觸」</strong><br />\n<br />\n美國與中國貿易爭端升級之際，CNBC周五引述華府一名高級官員稱，兩國政府近期就貿易問題「零接觸」。<br />\n<br />\n這名美國官員稱，過往數天，白宮與北京政府僅有一次通電話，但無助於解決貿易爭議，而在此之前的一個月時間，兩國高層陷入靜默狀態。當被問及兩國近日維持哪種層級的接觸時，這名官員作出「零」的手勢。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普首席經濟顧問庫德洛，周五稍早時在白宮對記者表示，美中兩國有保持「最高層次」的溝通，但相關磋商陷入停滯。庫德洛稱，「我一直有參與眾多美中談判，但不是最近，因為最近沒有，我不知道中國官員在幹甚麼。」<br />\n<br />\n中國國務院關稅稅則委員會周五公布最新決定，對原產於美國的5207個稅目進口商品加徵5%至25%的關稅，涉及自美進口貿易額約600億美元，實施日期將另行公布。"},{"pid":"bff6a519ca2446df5a53f32891be0601cbc01b68","tid":766650,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T18:08:32.000Z","msg":"睇tvb仲點講緩和之際 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aab328ab5c9d6d31e0223e2fa6442713e01bfde","tid":766650,"uid":41245,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T22:19:06.000Z","msg":"成份一份8項嘅要求<br />\n支那一項都冇諗住做<br />\n噉傾條毛？<br />\n同連登仔話自己理性一樣"},{"pid":"84e2d4bbe566be1eb6a2046286c01a0ed944fd45","tid":766650,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T23:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cb3dc5186e5ab2045c74f65258efd800c9cbc70","tid":766650,"uid":4285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T23:16:53.000Z","msg":"中國班高層<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n接觸都係俾人撚"},{"pid":"cd224b41505ff98d15b8e6dcd9106c53550e33de","tid":766650,"uid":51932,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T23:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media2.giphy.com/media/l3q2Zj2UUswAtUfC0/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia2.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fl3q2Zj2UUswAtUfC0%2Fgiphy.gif&h=2ca68166&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3c3dc11f4da866798f7947394d57649c3128928","tid":766650,"uid":175865,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T23:21:23.000Z","msg":"侵侵好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8cc3bcf7b9c